Package: batchscr
Type: Package
Title: Batch Script Helpers
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Sherry Zhao
Maintainer: Sherry Zhao<sxzhao@gwu.edu>
BugReports: https://github.com/sherrisherry/batchscr/issues
Description: Handy frameworks, such as error handling and log generation, for batch scripts.
	Use case: in scripts running in remote servers, set error handling mechanism for downloading and uploading and record operation log.
